name: Otoris M Generative
description:
Introducing the major players within the ranks of Generatives and Disruptives at Gormenghast.

Otoris M Generative – a primary engager coupled with Otoris, she is very strong against the Cernu Disruptives as she holds not one but multiple universes in her formidable self.

It is from Otoris’s genes that was generated Noden – one of the first Oracles in millennia. Together they are unbeatable as Noden, aware of what is to happen and where, is able to relay that information to Otoris M G who is able to place her multi-verse anywhere in space or time, thus causing cataclysmic conditions for whom they choose to target.

Together they work as spies and assassins and you’ll never know if they’re coming for you, not even after they have been.

That is, until Noden is kidnapped.

PNG 4800 x 4800 || December 12th 2021 || Dark Art digital painting – expanding the Gormenghast origin universe
